    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, those are good starting points. can you expand on the 'rule of law' and 'national sovereignty' points? my students need to be able to explain exactly why a country has a moral or legal right to strictly control its borders, rather than just saying 'it's the law.' can you give me some deeper philosophical or legal reasoning they can use in their opening statements?",
